(2467) -Djukic,N (2503) Novi Sad 2009. Here I like} Nb6 18. f5 Nc4 $1 19. Bxc4 Rfc8 
20. b3 b5 {when Black will regain the piece and White's advantage (if any) is 
negligible. As Black you must often be satisfied with such opening conclusions, but 
if this line bores you feel free to try the more complex 13...Nc6!? instead!} *

