the position. Black is up a pawn but has a few weaknesses to tend to (c4, e6, the 
a1-h8 diagonal). Black is fine here, but precision is required.} a6 {Xiong, J 
(2523)-Bartholomew, J (2449) Dayton 2015. I later drew this game but had to suffer a 
bit. The engine's recommendation of 18...b5! is better.} *

