pawns on e6 and f7 the bishop is'biting on granite.'} Bb4 $5 {Played by GM Fridman.} 
10. a3 Bxc3+ 11. bxc3 Qa5 12. Bd2 Nbd7 13. O-O O-O 14. Bd3 e5 $5 {Ringoir,T 
(2399)-Fridman, R (2456) Germany 2009} *

