Black over in the center with d4-d5.} Nxe4 14. Qxe4 Qe7 15. d5 exd5 16. Qxe7+ Bxe7 
{This looks like another route to equality, e.g.} 17. cxd5 Kd7 $1 18. dxc6+ Kxc6 19. 
Kb1 b6 20. Rhe1 Rhe8 *

