10...Nbd7, then White has 11. c6!}) 11. a4 b4 12. O-O Bb7 13. Nd2 Nxc5 14. Nc4 
{Mazi,L (2402)-Vukovic,Z (2439) Bled 2003} a5 $1 $15 *

