find a nice home on b4 in the future.} 7. h3 Bf5 8. O-O e6 9. Re1 Be7 10. Nh4 $2 
{meet a cute refutation:} Bxh3 $1 11. gxh3 Qd4 $19 {hitting both h4 and c4.} *

