1. e4 d5 {Believe it or not, you will encounter more than a few players who will 
decline the proffered d-pawn! Maybe they're suspicious of Black's kind gesture? :)} 
2. Nc3 dxe4 3. Nxe4 {now Black has a choice: Another acceptable option is Nc6. My 
preference is for Qd5!?} Qd5 $5 {This is a cheeky sortie that I've employed over the 
years. The idea is to encourage Ne4-c3 and transpose to a main-line Scandinavian! 
Funnily enough, on} 4. Nc3 {Black can repeat with} Qd8 {or opt for a different 
variation like 3...Qd6 or 3...Qa5.} *

