helpful nudge, possibly...menacing. ..b7-b5 while controlling the b5 square. The 
upside of this move is demonstrated after} 8. a4 Nf6 9. Bg5 Qd6 $1 {is excellent for 
Black according to GM Bauer in'Play the Scandinavian'} *

