Scandinavian'.} 5. h3 Bh5 6. g4 $5 Bg6 7. e6 {Otherwise Black will play 7...e6 
himself.} fxe6 8. Ne5 {This is Starc,C (2155)-Drozdov,A Eger 1994. Here GM Bauer 
proposes the innovative line} Nf6 $5 9. Nxc6 Qb6 $1 10. Nxa7+ Kf7 {when Black will 
recover the piece with a double-edged fight ahead.} *

